{"tid":291811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新班子最快今登場羅致光退黨　料掌勞福局","createTime":"2017-06-21T00:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T02:18:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1508497d5f8fd386900452b7d3e759d4f20cb83b","tid":291811,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:55:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20063450&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170621\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20063450%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170621&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2B8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=f5f98201\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20063450%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170621&h=6d9e3a43\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20063450&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170621</a><br />\n<br />\n新班子最快今登場<br />\n羅致光退黨　料掌勞福局<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】候任特首林鄭月娥的新班子最快今天登場，據了解，國務院料於今早宣佈任命第五屆特區主要官員，林鄭下午會率領新一屆司、局長與傳媒會面。新班子中料只有羅致光（圖）是非公務員及現屆官員外的新面孔，盛傳或掌勞工及福利局的羅昨晚向民主黨申請退黨，獲該黨中委會接納。<br />\n<br />\n劉業強或入行會<br />\n<br />\n民主黨接納羅的退黨申請後發表聲明指，感謝羅過去對黨及民主運動的無私奉獻，「今天雖然各奔前程，在未來的崗位和角色將有所不同，仍望他能發揮所長，在新崗位繼續為香港發聲」。<br />\n而羅致光昨接受now新聞台訪問時談及取消強積金對沖等問題，指長期服務金及遣散費屬失業保障，與強積金沒有直接關係，政府應趁財力充裕時盡快解決對沖問題。他亦建議取消標準稅率，指政府坐擁盈餘，目前毋須加稅，但可考慮增設非本地人的物業增值稅及空置稅。<br />\n另外，以鄉議局代表身份加入行會的張學明昨稱因身體問題求退，已向林鄭說明個人意願。消息稱，鄉議局前主席劉皇發兒子、現任鄉議局主席劉業強料接棒入行會。<br />\n■記者許偉賢<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2B8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=04a548fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n拆局：須向北京「交功課」<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;2小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n團體抗議　斥標時「689拖到777」<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;2小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n林鄭擬重推國教幼兒開始培養「我是中國人」概念<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;2小時前"},{"pid":"d14950bfa65752bea6af59745766f094815ef839","tid":291811,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170621/large/a0103a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170621%2Flarge%2Fa0103a.gif&h=32ab1dea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ca5bf54401a6c9e9c35863a4902ef3e8a06ee8f","tid":291811,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:58:57.000Z","msg":"民主黨專出賣建制人材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a37bb6c9890d52e4158eb7ced2c989c55cc8ae","tid":291811,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民主黨專出建制人材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d7ae60c56b34e2597c66c912651eb0c55e5e84a0","tid":291811,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:18:41.000Z","msg":"第幾個反骨仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}